  <description>
    <p>**This wrapper is not verified by, affiliated with, or supported by RemNote.**</p>
    <p>RemNote is the all-in-one tool for thinking and learning. It combines
      note-taking, spaced repetition, and knowledge management in a single
      platform to help you learn faster and think better.</p>
